entry.title: splinedrive/kianRiscV
entry.summary: KianRISC-V! No RISC-V, no fun! RISC-V CPU with strong design rules and unittested! CPU you can trust! kianv rv32im risc-v a hdmi soc with harris computer architecture in verilog: multicycle, singlecycle and 5-stage pipelining Processor. Multicycle Soc with firmware that runs raytracer, mandelbrot, 3d hdmi gfx, dma controller, linux soc included, .
